luakitch/Adhere.package_name: "release:publish": "node -e \"const { version } = require('./package.json'); const tagName = 'v' + version; const setupFilePath = `dist/Adhere-Setup-${version}.exe`; const blockmapFilePath = `${setupFilePath}.blockmap`; const ymlFilePath = 'dist/latest.yml'; const { execSync } = require('child_process'); console.log(`\\\\n📦 Preparing to publish release ${tagName} to Adhere-Releases...`); try { console.log('  - Creating git tag...'); execSync(`git tag ${tagName}`, { stdio: 'inherit' }); console.log('  - Pushing git tag to origin...'); execSync(`git push origin ${tagName}`, { stdio: 'inherit' }); console.log('  - Creating GitHub release and uploading assets...'); execSync(`gh release create ${tagName} --repo luakitch/Adhere-Releases --target main --generate-notes --title \\\"Adhere ${tagName}\\\" \\\"${setupFilePath}\\\" \\\"${blockmapFilePath}\\\" \\\"${ymlFilePath}\\\"`, { stdio: 'inherit' }); console.log(`\\\\n✅ Successfully published release ${tagName}!`); } catch (e) { console.error(`\\\\n❌ Publishing failed. Please check the error message above. Make sure you have committed all your changes and are authenticated with 'gh auth login'.`); process.exit(1); }\"",
"release:win": "rimraf dist && npm run build:win && npm run sign:win && npm run release:checksum && npm run release:publish",
